14:30.633 --> 14:32.600
- On the corner,
don't you have some way

14:32.667 --> 14:36.033
to measure a fella's loyalty?

14:36.100 --> 14:37.667
- Yeah, we got something
like that.

14:37.734 --> 14:39.934
What? Fuck this nigga, yo!
[overlapping shouting]

14:40.000 --> 14:41.667
