14:44.166 --> 14:46.834
All right, stop, stop!
All right, stop!

14:46.900 --> 14:50.867
♪ ♪

14:50.934 --> 14:54.867
Come on, motherfucker.
Get up, nigga.

14:54.934 --> 14:57.734
Look at that.
One love, one love.

14:57.800 --> 14:58.834
- [laughs]
- Yeah!

14:58.900 --> 14:59.967
- Yeah!
