any violent behavior,

16:54.900 --> 16:58.433
so, uh, yeah, you're ready.

16:58.500 --> 17:01.600
- The question is, do I
put you back in Emerald City?

17:01.667 --> 17:03.967
- I hope yes.

17:04.033 --> 17:07.166
But if you don't,
I understand.

17:07.233 --> 17:09.266
It's because of the trouble
I caused.

17:09.333 --> 17:12.066
- There are plenty of guys in
there have issues against you.

17:12.133 --> 17:15.400
- I will apologize
to each person that I've hurt.

17:15.467 --> 17:17.633
Starting with you, McManus.

17:17.700 --> 17:20.133
♪ ♪

17:20.200 --> 17:21.200
I'm sorry.

17:21.266 --> 17:23.934
♪ ♪

17:24.000 --> 17:26.967
- Apology accepted.
