17:27.033 --> 17:29.000
♪ ♪

17:29.066 --> 17:31.967
[buzzer]

17:32.033 --> 17:34.000
- Hey, look, Adebisi's back.

17:34.066 --> 17:36.300
What's up, Africa?
- Is he okay?

17:36.367 --> 17:37.800
- Back from the bush.

17:37.867 --> 17:44.900
♪ ♪

17:46.233 --> 17:50.300
