18:03.834 --> 18:08.433
By taking Jara's life,
you saved mine.

18:08.500 --> 18:10.433
♪ ♪

18:10.500 --> 18:11.967
Thank you.

18:12.033 --> 18:15.166
♪ ♪

18:15.233 --> 18:18.233
