18:49.834 --> 18:52.533
- Come on, all that bullshit
about Africa and trust?

18:52.600 --> 18:55.967
[scoffs] He's setting us up.
- Well, that remains to be seen.

18:56.033 --> 18:57.667
- Fuck that--I'm twistin'
the shit first chance I get--

18:57.734 --> 19:00.400
- Nah, you don't touch him
unless I give the say-so.

19:00.467 --> 19:01.800
- [clicks tongue]
Bullshit!

19:01.867 --> 19:05.166
Fuck what you say!
- Nah, this is not bullshit.

19:05.233 --> 19:07.633
You take a walk.

19:07.700 --> 19:13.633
♪ ♪

19:13.700 --> 19:16.400
- Skipper, why not
let him kill Adebisi?

19:16.467 --> 19:18.367
It's no skin off of us.

19:18.433 --> 19:21.967
- You know,
Wrangler's very cocky.

19:22.033 --> 19:25.867
If our Nigerian friend's
change of heart is real,

19:25.934 --> 19:29.166
he could be worth plenty
to us alive.

19:29.233 --> 19:30.767
- Come on, guys, move it.
[claps once]

19:30.834 --> 19:32.700
You guys are moving like a bunch
of turtles this morning.

19:32.767 --> 19:34.633
Come on.
- Hey, Adebisi.

19:34.700 --> 19:36.533
What are you up to?
- Nothing.

19:36.600 --> 19:38.333
- Look, this is me
you're talking to.

19:38.400 --> 19:39.800
You're gonna tell me
you're not gonna get revenge

19:39.867 --> 19:41.867
on the wops and Wangler?

19:41.934 --> 19:43.300
- That's right.
- Look.

19:43.367 --> 19:45.500
Whatever drugs they had you on
in the psych ward,

19:45.567 --> 19:48.200
I hope you brought some
to share.

19:49.633 --> 19:52.667
- Come on, man.
Watch where you going.

19:52.734 --> 19:54.200
- Excuse me.

19:54.266 --> 19:56.266
♪ ♪

19:56.333 --> 19:58.900
- He don't look
so fuckin' tough to me.

19:58.967 --> 20:06.033
♪ ♪

20:16.700 --> 20:18.100
- Ah!
[knife slashes]

20:19.266 --> 20:21.166
- [screams]

20:22.734 --> 20:26.033
- Move it, Adebisi.

20:26.100 --> 20:27.934
- Okay, boss.

20:28.000 --> 20:29.433
[whistles melody]

20:29.500 --> 20:31.066
[tone beeps]

20:32.734 --> 20:33.867
- They changed the name?

20:33.934 --> 20:35.533
- Yeah, catchy, huh?

20:35.600 --> 20:38.033
Sign in, please.

20:38.100 --> 20:40.467
- My, uh, father
used to work here.

20:40.533 --> 20:42.500
Maybe you knew him?

20:42.567 --> 20:44.033
Samuel Hughes.

20:44.100 --> 20:46.066
- Sammy Hughes!
