20:46.133 --> 20:48.333
You Sammy's kid?
- Uh-huh.

20:48.400 --> 20:52.467
- Your dad, he's, uh...
still missed.

20:54.200 --> 20:55.400
- Thank you.

20:55.467 --> 20:57.800
- So, what brings you back?

20:57.867 --> 20:59.700
- I'm here to see Leo,
my warden,

20:59.767 --> 21:01.166
about applying for a job.

21:01.233 --> 21:04.100
- No. Absolutely not.

21:04.166 --> 21:06.467
- Why?
I completed CO training.

21:06.533 --> 21:08.233
Came in second in my class.

21:08.300 --> 21:09.767
- Does your mother know
about this?

21:09.834 --> 21:11.734
- I want to surprise her.
- [laughs] Oh.

21:11.800 --> 21:12.967
You're gonna surprise her,
all right.

21:13.033 --> 21:14.600
You're gonna give her
heart failure.

21:14.667 --> 21:16.834
- Not if I have your support.

21:16.900 --> 21:19.567
Leo, after Dad died,
you were always there for me.

21:19.633 --> 21:21.133
Be there for me now.

21:21.200 --> 21:22.734
- When the hell
did you grow up?

21:22.800 --> 21:24.100
The last time I looked,
you were seven.

21:24.166 --> 21:26.800
- Come on, Leo, listen--
- Clayton...

21:26.867 --> 21:29.467
look, I promised your father
I'd watch out for you.

21:29.533 --> 21:32.133
- I want to be a CO.

21:32.200 --> 21:34.266
Like you.
Like Dad.

21:34.333 --> 21:36.734
- Clayton--
- Leo, if you don't hire me,

21:36.800 --> 21:38.767
another prison will.

21:38.834 --> 21:41.066
♪ ♪

21:41.133 --> 21:42.500
- [groans]

21:42.567 --> 21:46.066
