to pass along to you.

22:08.900 --> 22:12.934
"Be aware and beware."

22:13.000 --> 22:18.500
My own little addendum
is "Be fair."

22:18.567 --> 22:21.166
Again...welcome.

22:21.233 --> 22:24.033
[applause]

22:24.100 --> 22:26.700
- Some speech.
- What, you didn't like it?

22:26.767 --> 22:28.033
- Sounds like you said
the same thing

22:28.100 --> 22:30.066
