29:47.800 --> 29:50.000
You don't want to know
what I'm bringing in?

29:50.066 --> 29:51.900
- Your business.

29:51.967 --> 29:54.467
- Besides, you'll know when
you scan the box, right?

29:54.533 --> 29:56.834
- Right.

29:56.900 --> 29:58.600
- I cleared it with Hoyt.

29:58.667 --> 30:00.000
He's gonna make sure
our package gets through

30:00.066 --> 30:01.934
without anyone knowing, okay?

30:02.033 --> 30:03.967
- Okay.

30:04.033 --> 30:09.200
♪ ♪

30:09.266 --> 30:10.200
[scanner clicks]

30:10.266 --> 30:13.900
♪ ♪

30:13.967 --> 30:15.367
